TestClassGenerator

public TestClassGenerator()
Create a new TestClassGenerator with the default options.

TestClassGenerator

public TestClassGenerator(boolean the_dry_run,
                          boolean the_no_gen,
                          Logger the_logger,
                          ProtectionLevel the_protection_level,
                          boolean the_test_inherited_methods,
                          boolean the_test_deprecated_methods,
                          boolean the_use_reflection,
                          boolean the_use_children,
                          String the_rac_version)
Create a new TestClassGenerator with the given options.

Parameters:
the_dry_run - A flag indicating whether this is a dry run (i.e., whether files will be generated or not).
the_no_gen - A flag indicating whether this is a no-generation run (i.e., whether we're doing it only to figure out what files would have been created).
the_logger - The logger to use to generate output.
the_protection_level - The maximum protection level for which to generate method tests.
the_test_inherited_methods - A flag indicating whether to test inherited methods.
the_test_deprecated_methods - A flag indicating whether to test deprecated methods.
the_use_reflection - A flag indicating whether to generate test data that uses reflection at runtime.
the_rac_version - The RAC version to generate test classes for.
